snippet.title: Fruitbus Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: A journey of flavors and friendships awaits you in your cozy, customizable food truck! Fruitbus is a cute culinary adventure in an open world where taste is everything. Upgrade your trusty truck and visit a whole world of new destinations together. https://store.steampowered.com/app/2484130/Fruitbus/ #indiegames #cookinggames #cozygames
